Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-a)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是From Beyond的Beyond Flamenco
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:55.76,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(640,372)}虛偽的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快現出原形來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別按照字面意思理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是說我們是真正的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我們的關係和兄弟極其相似
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼和我長得一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自說自話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來 是你長得和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是正 我是邪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說最容易理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你為什麼自稱佛朗明哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就會明白的 到時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事之後再問你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是領隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停止裝置 並讓所有人投降！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我說倒是無所謂 但是我覺得不會有人聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個窗口罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗口？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,65000個From Beyond的集體意見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是集體意識的代言人罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰敗之後就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說 我自己也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征服世界之後要怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何統治？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑六萬多人根本對付不了六十億人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界和平也同理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要人類還是人類 任何理由都能引起戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些話你都聽煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為這種不可能得到的東西而戰是毫無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的…這麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產生這種念頭的瞬間 就變成這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你還有那些傢伙所做的事都毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同之處就是為何瘋狂 如何瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂到什麼地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這個階段很快就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經放棄這個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也遲早會被人打敗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難聽的話我就不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全聽不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一能說的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我是自己想要保護大家才去保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是自己想要保護日本才去保護日本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意義之後再去想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的理由對這種荒謬的戰鬥而言恰到好處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想做所以去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發動攻擊的原因說到底也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說出來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅斧戰士 這究竟是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 但是危機還沒有散去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamenger 回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond Flamenco自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 日本毀滅裝置仍在運作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我現在立刻安排拆除小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣裝置就會到達地脈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我去申請轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:05:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個方法了 要先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這方法的成功率是最高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們去吧 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 你們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamenger 拯救日本吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Robo 所有裝置解放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞它！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Impact！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Kick！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Knee Drop！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…切腹先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人已經被消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放市民們出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您接下來要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去富士山腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為同伴們正在那裡等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:07:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 如果其中有一位叫武士…Flamen Red的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我向他轉達一句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去轉達吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生還者的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介錯號 GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 快給我說明情況！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 Flamenger正在阻止日本毀滅裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們停手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會請美軍進行轟炸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣可能就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總指揮是我 快服從命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒我直言 總理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您現在要阻止Flamenger 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們是不會袖手旁觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？你什麼意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個出故障了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能聽到雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Elbow！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞穴也正在崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會被活埋的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果不在這裡阻止它 會到達熔岩層的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點就可以收拾掉這個龐然大物了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下那一招了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個太消耗能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那麼做了 我們就無法從這些沙土和瓦礫中脫身了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是關鍵時刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Drill！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽頭就要用鑽頭來對付！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamenger！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就猜到會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Punch？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F Flamenger！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失禮啊 我的逃脫計畫是不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 Flamen Robo…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\shad0\bord3\c&H443425&\3c&HC6C0AF&}謝謝你們給我們帶來了和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\shad0\fs32\c&H595040&\3c&HB3A898&}內閣府 全國英雄聯盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那麼 你為什麼自稱佛朗明哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「到時候你就會明白的 到時候」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛朗明哥武士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從美國來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Justice
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.…Justice？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我漂洋過海來向你傳達真相
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人和師父很像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是你的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間正義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖投降吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是來找我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼拿槍對著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許提問！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五秒之內雙手抱頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 正義的英雄有幾種應對方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A 乖乖投降 為自己辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B 拒絕投降 走為上計
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是誤會 所以我選擇A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是種正確的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我會選擇B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種上來就要打架的態度是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說No的時候就要堅決說No
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的開槍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說對方是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是公安的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公安？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}註：警察組織中主要負責處理威脅國家體制的事態的部門 工作一般具有保密性質
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼公務員會來找我麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛說過吧 你被騙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我會突破他們逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟著我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Justice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你就在這兒等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去教訓教訓他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們會開槍的 很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比紐約的十字路口安全多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Justice！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Tackle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Tackle！Tackle！Tackle！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好強…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 趁現在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你應該有很多疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些還是在秘密基地裡慢慢聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 逃走是我們的首要任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 這拖車最好還是塗得樸素點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著歌整理整理心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平 平靜不下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道大家有沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是接不了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重覆 我們已經把逃亡中的Flamenger困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他們赤手空拳也這麼難對付…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個專業人員 身後也要防範啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們可是拯救了日本吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼我們會突然被公安的人襲擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全摸不著頭腦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聯繫上領隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話和短信都還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信網已經被完全切斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來 領隊那邊也不好過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團體客人來了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人數太不科學了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下沒轍了 認栽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 逮捕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 還少一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青島蒼一不在這
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 青島在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們突然被包圍 逃得匆忙 哪顧得上那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道在這裡肯定等得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要問總理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是Flamen…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Blue！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是有這麼個團體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們應該解散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這打扮是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有同伴們引開追兵 我才能潛入基地變身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 放下吧放下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得有親愛的國民來拜訪我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我單獨和他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 那邊那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的支持率如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前是72%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,72%嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總理 如果你不能給出令人信服的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是總理大臣 我也不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要抓我們！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副來打架的氣勢可真讓人遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次想來見我的時候 記得先預約
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒想到…會 會是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心Flamenger的同伴們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看新聞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能會震驚 但這樣也能知道同伴們的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自導自演真是驚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑人已經接連…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條臨時新聞令社會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放臨時新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時新聞？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(634,502)}Flamenger有顛覆國家罪的嫌疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個月來所發生的From Beyond恐怖襲擊事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑為Flamenger小隊的自導自演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(634,502)}被逮捕的長官 要丈治嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師 師父！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\shad0\3c&H705A5C&\c&HFBFEDA&\pos(548,289)}嫌疑人團夥Flamenger所潛伏的工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該團夥與扮演敵方組織的From Beyond相互勾結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,580)\c&HFBFEDA&\bord4\shad0\3c&H705A5C&}被逮捕的Flamenger一行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引發眾多事件 擾亂社會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察已經逮捕Flamenger團夥的嫌疑人並聽取口供
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於政府在其中的牽涉 稍後奧崎總理將召開見面會說明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是胡編亂造！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是胡編亂造 如果大眾都相信就會變成真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳媒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱From Beyond的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是日本政府！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太扯了 他們為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了利用一次危機來統一民意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓政局變得有利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 這幾個月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於你們的活躍 內閣支持率上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多法案都通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們利用了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的國家也發生了同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括越南 伊拉克在內 國家想要轉移民眾視線的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會讓我和怪物 異形和宇宙人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義先生也是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這一切都是好萊塢的編劇和工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受政府委託而創作的虛構事件！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們犯了一個錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們太過正義了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了太多民眾的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越了英雄 成為了領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 你們可能會成為政府無法掌控的麻煩人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時他們會做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是 人更多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧 佛朗明哥武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒弱到會在這兒掛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來到了遊樂場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你們體驗體驗我的英雄秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Home Run！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Beam！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beam！Beam！Beam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的Police真是太孱弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都要吃大量穀物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大塊肉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用麻醉槍 真是不解風情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一連串事件都是沉迷虛擬作品的羽佐間正義為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過周密策劃 自導自演的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與政府完全無關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.89,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs45\pos(288,544)\frz356.287\3c&HFAF0E2&\c&H2C281E&}從羽佐間正義　　　\N家中所沒收的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.89,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs40\frz356.287\3c&HFAF0E2&\c&H2C281E&\pos(722,614)}與同謀的　\NBeyond Flamenco　　\N接觸的羽佐間正義\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很異常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:40.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs32\bord1\3c&HC3DBE5&\pos(404,378)}佛朗明哥武士\N策劃書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:40.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs32\3c&HC3DBE5&\frz357.484\pos(698,378)}佛朗明哥武士\N構思集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可大事不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了防範此類事件再次發生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們提出了非認可正義活動限製法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現已進入審議階段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 本著將國民安全作為第一考量的宗旨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分可疑人物均已被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未落網的只有羽佐間正義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本國將對他進行全國通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在這！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 佛朗明哥武士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是日本的敵人！
Comment: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ED2)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:25.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話筒對面熟悉的嗓音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.30,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去還算精神 讓我鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.27,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月台揮手道別之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.76,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記不清已有多久無緣相聚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.87,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上雙眼的夜航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:44.07,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像往常那樣在月亮背面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.98,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相約在23點碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:55.95,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遠萬里也要與你相見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.80,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以往讀過的聖埃克絮佩里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:03.74,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定漏掉了重要的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.58,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心裡確實存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:11.49,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:15.15,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起頭來笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:19.45,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靜仰望同一片夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:25.81,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從未分離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:33.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:41.17,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從未分離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:48.22,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:25.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受話器の向こう　聴き慣れた声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.30,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元気そうでほっとしたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.27,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会えなくなってどれくらいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.76,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を振ったホーム
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.87,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じ夜間飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:44.07,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもの月の裏で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.98,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23時　待ち合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:55.95,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな遠くても君と出逢える
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.80,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔読んだサンテグジュペリ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:03.74,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと肝心なことは見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.58,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の中　確かにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:11.49,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いろんな表情をした君が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:11.49,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(625,630)}かお
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:15.15,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俯かないで笑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:19.45,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと同じ夜空を見上げながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:19.45,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(610,630)}そら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:25.81,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離れ離れじゃないね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:33.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しくなんかないね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:41.17,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離れ離れじゃないね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:48.22,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しくなんかないね
